summary: Aimed at those looking to align their personal and startup goals, this section provides resources focused on growth, skills development, and effective communication. It offers courses that delve into identifying personal strengths and weaknesses, performing SWOT analyses, and formulating strategic asks to ensure better alignment and success.
excerpt: Discover your personal strengths and weaknesses, perform a SWOT analysis of your startup, and formulate a critical ask to communicate your needs and goals for better alignment and effectiveness.
